id: 028da368-7ba5-438f-b891-b8db4eb5aa90
---
graph TD
    Start([User: Generate Hypothesis]) --> SetGoal[BinderDesignSystem.set_research_goal]
    SetGoal --> ExtractSeq[Extract target_sequence & binder_sequence<br/>from research_goal]
    
    ExtractSeq --> SetConfig[Set research_plan_config in<br/>GenerationAgent.memory.metadata]
    SetConfig --> ConfigDetails["research_plan_config = &#123;<br/>  target_sequence: '...',<br/>  binder_sequence: '...',<br/>  task_type: 'binder_design'<br/>&#125;"]

    ConfigDetails --> GenHyp[BinderDesignSystem.generate_protein_hypothesis<br/>strategy parameter]
    
    GenHyp --> Strategy{Strategy Type?}
    
    Strategy -->|literature_exploration| Lit[_create_literature_exploration_prompt]
    Strategy -->|scientific_debate| Debate[_create_scientific_debate_prompt]
    Strategy -->|assumptions_identification| Assume[_create_assumptions_identification_prompt]
    Strategy -->|research_expansion| Expand[_create_research_expansion_prompt]
    Strategy -->|binder_gen| Binder[_create_binder_gen_prompt]
    
    Lit --> BuildPrompt[Build prompt with:<br/>- research_goal<br/>- target_sequence from config<br/>- binder_sequence from config]
    Debate --> BuildPrompt
    Assume --> BuildPrompt
    Expand --> BuildPrompt
    Binder --> BuildPrompt
    
    BuildPrompt --> Step1[STEP 1: Generate Initial Hypothesis]
    
    Step1 --> LLMCall1[LLMInterface.generate_with_json_output<br/>mode: json_object<br/>NO tool calling yet]
    
    LLMCall1 --> Schema["JSON Schema:<br/>&#123;<br/>  hypothesis: &#123;title, content, ...&#125;,<br/>  binder_data: &#123;<br/>    target_sequence,<br/>    proposed_peptides: [&#123;<br/>      sequence,<br/>      source: 'literature'|'homology'|'de-novo',<br/>      rationale,<br/>      confidence_score<br/>    &#125;],<br/>    literature_references<br/>  &#125;,<br/>  generation_strategy,<br/>  explanation<br/>&#125;"]

    Schema --> Response1[LLM Response:<br/>Structured hypothesis with<br/>literature/homology/de-novo peptides]
    
    Response1 --> CreateMeta[Create metadata dict:<br/>- title, key_novelty_aspects<br/>- testable_predictions<br/>- binder_data<br/>- generation_strategy]
    
    CreateMeta --> CheckTools{Tool Registry<br/>Available?}
    
    CheckTools -->|No| CreateHyp[Create ResearchHypothesis<br/>with metadata]
    CheckTools -->|Yes| Step2[STEP 2: Ask LLM About Tools]
    
    Step2 --> ToolPrompt["Tool Decision Prompt:<br/>'You proposed N peptides from literature.<br/>Would you like to use computational<br/>design tools to generate additional<br/>binder sequences?<br/><br/>Available tools:<br/>- bindcraft_design'"]

    ToolPrompt --> LLMCall2[LLMInterface.generate_with_tools<br/>mode: function_calling<br/>tools: bindcraft_design schema]

    LLMCall2 --> ToolDecision{LLM Decision?}
    
    ToolDecision -->|finish_reason: stop| NoTools[❌ LLM decided NOT to use tools<br/>Log reasoning]
    ToolDecision -->|finish_reason: tool_calls| YesTools[✅ LLM decided to USE tools<br/>Extract tool_calls array]
    
    NoTools --> CreateHyp
    
    YesTools --> ParseCalls[Parse tool_calls:<br/>- name: 'bindcraft_design'<br/>- arguments: &#123;<br/>    target_sequence,<br/>    num_sequences,<br/>    temperature,<br/>    device, mpnn_model, etc.<br/>  &#125;]
    
    ParseCalls --> ExecLoop[For each tool_call]
    
    ExecLoop --> ExecTool[ToolRegistry.execute_tool<br/>tool_name, **arguments]
    
    ExecTool --> BindCraftTool[BindCraftTool.execute]
    
    BindCraftTool --> MergeConfig[Merge config defaults with<br/>tool call arguments:<br/>- Tool args override config<br/>- Config provides defaults for:<br/>  device, mpnn_model, mpnn_weights,<br/>  proteinmpnn_path, num_rounds]
    
    MergeConfig --> TaskParams["task_params = &#123;<br/>  target_sequence: from tool_call,<br/>  num_seq: tool_call OR config,<br/>  device: tool_call OR config,<br/>  mpnn_model: tool_call OR config,<br/>  mpnn_weights: tool_call OR config,<br/>  proteinmpnn_path: tool_call OR config,<br/>  qc_kwargs: from config<br/>&#125;"]

    TaskParams --> RunBindCraft[BindCraftAgent.run_design_cycle<br/>task_params]
    
    RunBindCraft --> BindCraftFlow[BindCraft Workflow:<br/>1. Initialize Chai folding<br/>2. Initialize ProteinMPNN<br/>3. Launch agents via Manager<br/>4. PeptideDesignCoordinator.run_full_workflow<br/>5. Design-Fold-Filter rounds]
    
    BindCraftFlow --> BindCraftResult["BindCraft Result:<br/>&#123;<br/>  success: true,<br/>  top_sequences: [&#123;<br/>    sequence,<br/>    plddt, pae, energy<br/>  &#125;],<br/>  num_sequences_generated,<br/>  best_energy<br/>&#125;"]

    BindCraftResult --> FormatResult[BindCraftTool._format_results<br/>Extract top 5 sequences]
    
    FormatResult --> ReturnResult[Return formatted result to<br/>GenerationAgent]
    
    ReturnResult --> IncorpResults[Incorporate tool results into metadata:<br/>Add to binder_data.proposed_peptides]
    
    IncorpResults --> AddPeptides["For each top_sequence:<br/>proposed_peptides.append&#40;&#123;<br/>  sequence: seq_data.sequence,<br/>  source: 'computational:bindcraft',<br/>  rationale: 'Generated by BindCraft...',<br/>  confidence_score: plddt/100,<br/>  tool_metadata: &#123;plddt, pae, ptm, i_ptm&#125;<br/>&#125;&#41;"]

    AddPeptides --> SetFlags[Set metadata flags:<br/>- tool_calls_made: true<br/>- tool_call_count: N]
    
    SetFlags --> CreateHyp
    
    CreateHyp --> FinalHyp["ResearchHypothesis:<br/>- content: hypothesis text<br/>- summary: hypothesis summary<br/>- metadata: &#123;<br/>    binder_data: &#123;<br/>      target_sequence,<br/>      proposed_peptides: [<br/>        &#123;source: 'literature', ...&#125;,<br/>        &#123;source: 'homology', ...&#125;,<br/>        &#123;source: 'computational:bindcraft', ...&#125;<br/>      ]<br/>    &#125;,<br/>    tool_calls_made: true<br/>  &#125;"]

    FinalHyp --> Convert[Convert to ProteinHypothesis<br/>via from_unified_hypothesis]
    
    Convert --> Return([Return ProteinHypothesis<br/>to User])
    
    style Start fill:#e1f5ff
    style Return fill:#e1f5ff
    style Step1 fill:#fff4e1
    style Step2 fill:#fff4e1
    style YesTools fill:#d4edda
    style NoTools fill:#f8d7da
    style Schema fill:#f0f0f0
    style ConfigDetails fill:#f0f0f0
    style ToolPrompt fill:#f0f0f0
    style TaskParams fill:#f0f0f0
    style BindCraftResult fill:#f0f0f0
    style AddPeptides fill:#f0f0f0
    style FinalHyp fill:#d4edda